---
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Boss | Professional Portfolio</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; background-color:#111; color:#E0E0E0; line-height:1.6;">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="hero" style="text-align:center; padding:6rem 2rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:3rem; color:#32CD32; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Boss</h1>
      <p style="color:#00CED1; margin-bottom:2rem;">Cloud, IoT, Smart Home, Automation</p>
      <a href="#resume" style="padding:0.75rem 2rem; border:2px solid #32CD32; color:#32CD32; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; border-radius:6px;">View Resume / CV</a>
    </section>

    <!-- About & Skills -->
    <section id="about" style="padding:4rem 2rem; max-width:900px; margin:auto;">
      <h2 style="color:#32CD32; margin-bottom:1rem;">About Me</h2>
      <p>Engineering enthusiast specializing in cloud computing, IoT, DevOps, and smart home automation. Experienced in building scalable systems, automating workflows, and implementing innovative solutions.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#32CD32; margin-top:2rem;">Technical Skills</h3>
      <ul style="list-style:none; margin-top:1rem; padding:0;">
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin-right:0.5rem;">Python, Bash, Linux</li>
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin-right:0.5rem;">Docker, Portainer</li>
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin-right:0.5rem;">AWS & GCP</li>
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin-right:0.5rem;">Home Assistant, ESPHome, Zigbee</li>
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin-right:0.5rem;">Networking, VLANs, Tailscale VPN</li>
        <li style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block;">Monitoring: Grafana, Prometheus, Kuma</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience / Projects -->
    <section id="experience" style="padding:4rem 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color:#32CD32; text-align:center;">Experience & Projects</h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px,1fr)); gap:2rem; margin-top:2rem; max-width:1000px; margin:auto;">

        <div style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:1.5rem; border-radius:8px;">
          <h3>Smart Home Automation</h3>
          <p>Local-first Home Assistant system integrating Zigbee, ESPHome, and IR devices. Focus on automation, energy efficiency, and maintainable architecture.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:1.5rem; border-radius:8px;">
          <h3>Cloud Lab</h3>
          <p>GCP Debian VMs with Docker, Portainer, monitoring stacks (Grafana + Kuma), and Tailscale VPN access for secure experiments.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border:1px solid #32CD32; padding:1.5rem; border-radius:8px;">
          <h3>Vehicle Camera System</h3>
          <p>Integrated blind spot, reverse, and IR front-facing cameras with remote ignition starter and system monitoring.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Resume / CV -->
    <section id="resume" style="padding:4rem 2rem; text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="color:#32CD32;">Resume / CV</h2>
      <p>Download my full professional resume for detailed experience, certifications, and projects:</p>
      <a href="/files/Boss_Resume.pdf" style="padding:0.75rem 2rem; border:2px solid #32CD32; color:#32CD32; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; border-radius:6px;">Download PDF</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; border-top:1px solid #32CD32; margin-top:4rem;">
      <p>Last updated: Mar 5, 2026</p>
      <div>
        <a href="https://github.com/sqhomelab" target="_blank" style="color:#32CD32; margin:0 1rem; text-decoration:none;">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" style="color:#32CD32; margin:0 1rem; text-decoration:none;">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="mailto:email@example.com" style="color:#32CD32; margin:0 1rem; text-decoration:none;">Email</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
